comment: Jordan (LAC) makes contact with Howard's (HOU) body during his dunk attempt.
Harden (HOU) commits a take foul on Crawford (LAC).

Harden (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Redick (LAC) as he prepares to trap him near mid-court. He does not commit a take foul.
[Incidental or immaterial] Terry (HOU) grabs and holds Redick (LAC), affecting his FOM during the inbounds play.
Terry (HOU) commits a take foul on Redick (LAC).
Mbah a Moute (LAC) grabs Ariza (HOU) and affects his RSBQ.

Los Angeles inbounds the ball and their head coach does not ask the slot official for a time-out. The slot official prevents the head coach from stepping on to the court during play.
Harden (HOU) legally contests Paul's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Crawford (LAC) and Thornton (HOU) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
Howard (HOU) sets the screen on Redick (LAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Pierce (LAC) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Ariza's (HOU) driving layup attempt.

Jordan (LAC) obtains a legal guarding position and jumps vertically as he contests Harden's (HOU) driving layup attempt. There is incidental contact on the play that does not affect Harden's shot attempt.
